
mineflayer - Minecraft client and bot.

Current features:
 * logs in without authentication
 * renders some of the actual map with OpenGL
 * doesn't crash for 10 seconds or so

Planned features:
 * bot that builds stuff

Installing Ogre 1.7 in Ubunut:
    sudo apt-add-repository ppa:ogre-team/ogre
    sudo apt-get update 
    sudo apt-get install libogre-dev 

Setting up build:
 1. Run ./extract_resources <path_to_minecraft.jar>
 2. Open .pro file in QtCreator
 3. Build
 4. Manually copy resources/ to build directory
    * resources/

